00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:31,217
>> It's fun to watch that physiology play
out in real life [LAUGH]

363
00:24:31,217 --> 00:24:32,120
>> Yeah, yeah, but my other,

364
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:34,095
my other statement is choose your parents
wisely.

365
00:24:34,095 --> 00:24:35,200
>> [LAUGH] Exactly.

