371
00:24:53,248 --> 00:24:59,190
>> [LAUGH]
>> So I, I weigh probably 165 now.

372
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:03,560
I weighed probably 175 pounds going to
Everest.

373
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:09,190
And I lost 12 kilos of weight.

374
00:25:09,190 --> 00:25:10,160
>> That's a lot of weight.

375
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:14,588
>> So I look like a stick figure coming
back.

376
00:25:14,588 --> 00:25:18,190
the, the muscle, just fuel wasting.

377
00:25:18,190 --> 00:25:22,780
You burn up lots and lots and lots of
calories, and it's just,

378
00:25:22,780 --> 00:25:29,120
it's impressively difficult to eat that
much to keep the weight on.

379
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:32,072
One's appetite suffers greatly.

