00:26:36,930 --> 00:26:44,910
categorized on our Everest trip was, we
had some funding from NASA to,

396
00:26:44,910 --> 00:26:50,570
to do some neurologic evaluation.

397
00:26:50,570 --> 00:26:54,898
So this is learning and memory.

398
00:26:54,898 --> 00:26:59,010
So psycho-motor evaluation.

