00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:35,290
post exposure data are getting back to but
not fully back to the baseline state.

407
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:38,270
The other thing that flies apart is,

408
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:42,850
learning of new knowledge under profound
hypoxia is appalling.

409
00:27:42,850 --> 00:27:46,980
I mean, you're back to, fairly rudimentary
skills.

